{"tid":1486673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做野喇手足！打著中國人嘅旗號 消費香港人嘅文化一華記茶餐廳","createTime":"2019-08-19T02:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T04:32:07.000Z","uid":54219,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c95f6a9aceb22c652968621351699395b22885e0","tid":1486673,"uid":54219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/19/102609_a405719febfa9181c43beaf16720d9d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F19%2F102609_a405719febfa9181c43beaf16720d9d5.png&h=6ce2f40b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/19/102715_cd8069aadcfd671a749a18fa7badc7d7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F19%2F102715_cd8069aadcfd671a749a18fa7badc7d7.png&h=e835ae17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4f8fR25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4f8fR25.png&h=ee008d53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSWhkSa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSWhkSa.png&h=b3cd3dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個光頭撚屌左一句港獨又一句暴徒 一次又一次抵毀香港人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成個垃圾page都係極深藍 <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/wahkeejapan/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fwahkeejapan%2F&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=3f59f0a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/wahkeejapan/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支持警察暴力 share埋咩我是中國人可以打我 <br />\n好心你係中國人就叫中國茶餐廳啦  真係狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點係！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲要好似冇乜人理個光頭閪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地就日日係到unun腳賺日本人巴打嘅錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌下架妹咁</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢啖氣我就呑唔落架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如大家諗下有咩辦法可以對付下個無髮無天佬<br />\n例如:有冇日本巴打可以打下日本食環個電話幫佢檢查下衛生咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9dd22075367e129e8a4f96d6e39bd0bfe96cc3b","tid":1486673,"uid":54219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:59:43.000Z","msg":"推車咁推1"},{"pid":"ad2a79dff6e2d7e62a47f2b42266b08517c9dd5d","tid":1486673,"uid":54219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:59:58.000Z","msg":"推車咁推2"},{"pid":"c7f517d1b52bb393961b837fa9f74406460d5a6b","tid":1486673,"uid":54219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:00:14.000Z","msg":"推車咁推3"},{"pid":"a8cd48464e0656aee6c682d6d3969a926133f2f8","tid":1486673,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:00:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5519a5a5af8eaf0f44655f046de287f49d7783e0","tid":1486673,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:00:49.000Z","msg":"之前報稅單野點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14066c5e60fa8d4f3448c92e95810f3fc12331a","tid":1486673,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁愛國就返中國啦咪搞日本"},{"pid":"6fe668c2e20116b36b03e9031d3611584d3ff854","tid":1486673,"uid":285433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5f4d6800702764e50554dc758feaf0a3d16b3f","tid":1486673